{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tantalus is a sci-fi anomaly game set on a mysterious spaceship. Take on the role of a patrol staff member, investigate anomalies throughout the ship, and report them to the control AI.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Patrol Staff Guide</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1. Do not overlook any anomalies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2. If an anomaly is detected, use the employee tablet to take a photo of the point and then move on to the next area.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3. The photo will be automatically submitted to the control AI, which will handle the issue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4. Complete patrol of Sector 1 through 8 before returning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">20 to 90 minutes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Controls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">WASD : Move</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">C: Toggle Camera ON/OFF</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">F: Open Door</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shift: Sprint</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ESC: Open Menu</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Adult Content Description</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game contains some scary monsters and aliens, blood, and supernatural horror elements.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Patrol Completed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3446210/02a8311cf2d1bb80ac9d7fc69690232a087a3576.jpg"},{"name":"The Last Crew Member","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3446210/688142753fb26a801ca1654ade49fc37663dedff.jpg"},{"name":"Eye Contact","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3446210/2689de21335138bf9cc4ba02d06d2b1aabcebec9.jpg"},{"name":"Where's Exit 8?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3446210/a